  <body>
    <section name="Save document type">
      <span class="shortdesc">How to save a document type.</span>

   <script type="text/javascript">
    leftpx=450;
    bottompx=350;
   </script>
   <div class='group'> 
    <div id='screenshot'><div>
     <img src="../../../../images/screenshots/cms_M9/inars/save_documenttype.png" alt='save document type screenshot'/> 
    </div></div>
    <p>
       Click on 'save and close' to save the changes to a document type and 'Close without saving'
       to discard the changes.
     </p>
   </div>

   <p>
    After  
    <a href='./add_markuped_text_to_documenttype.html'>adding</a>,
    <a href='./change_field_in_documenttype.html'>changing</a> or
    <a href='./remove_field_from_documenttype.html'>removing</a>
    fields from a documenttype, save the document type by clicking on the
    'save and close' button at the top of the document type tab.
    The changes can be discarded by clicking on the 'Close without saving'
    button. To make the document type available for authors,
    also <a href='./update_content.html'>update all content</a>.
   </p>

